graph LR
    Caikit["Caikit<br/>(AI Runtime Framework)"]

    %% Internal Platform Dependencies (consumers)
    CaikitNLP["caikit-nlp"] -->|registers NLP modules| Caikit
    CaikitTGIS["caikit-tgis-serving"] -->|wraps for TGIS backend| Caikit
    ModelMesh["Model Mesh<br/>(modelmesh-serving)"] -->|gRPC Unix socket<br/>model lifecycle| Caikit
    KServe["KServe"] -->|runs as predictor container| Caikit

    %% Core External Dependencies
    Caikit -->|gRPC server/client| grpcio["grpcio<br/>>=1.35.0,<2.0"]
    Caikit -->|data serialization| protobuf["protobuf<br/>>=3.19.0,<6"]
    Caikit -->|dynamic proto gen| py_to_proto["py-to-proto<br/>>=0.5.0,<0.6.0"]
    Caikit -->|config management| alchemy_config["alchemy-config<br/>>=1.1.1,<2.0.0"]

    %% Optional Runtime Dependencies
    Caikit -.->|HTTP API server| fastapi["FastAPI<br/>>=0.100,<1"]
    Caikit -.->|request validation| pydantic["Pydantic<br/>>=2.8.0,<3"]
    Caikit -.->|SSE streaming| sse_starlette["sse-starlette<br/>>=1.6.1,<3"]

    %% Optional Observability
    Caikit -.->|distributed tracing| otel["OpenTelemetry SDK<br/>>=1.24.0,<2"]
    Caikit -.->|metrics export| prometheus["prometheus_client<br/>>=0.12.0,<1.0"]

    %% External Services (Egress)
    Caikit -->|trace export<br/>4317/4318 TCP| OTELCollector["OpenTelemetry Collector"]
    Caikit -->|training data<br/>443/TCP HTTPS| S3["S3-compatible Storage"]
    Caikit -.->|distributed inference<br/>gRPC/HTTP| RemoteCaikit["Remote Caikit Servers"]

    %% Integration Points (incoming)
    Prometheus_Scrape["Prometheus"] -->|scrape metrics<br/>8086/TCP HTTP| Caikit

